summary¶

In this project, we focus on Gradient Boosting Decision Tree (GBDT) methodology, built XGBoost and LightGBM model,and compared their perfomance on Credit card Fraud dataset.

In practice, It's validated that lightGBM is 15 times faster than XGBoost, and achieved better accuracy based upon large-scale dataset.
